《'''深夜秀'''》（{{Lang-en|'''The Late Late Show'''}}）有時候英語又被稱作「The Late Late」<ref name="Look who just popped in for the Late Late">{{cite web|author=Jane Last|url=http://www.herald.ie/entertainment/around-town/look-who-just-popped-in-for-the-late-late-1902767.html|title=Look who just popped in for the Late Late|date=2 October 2009|accessdate=4 October 2009|publisher=[[Evening_Herald|Evening Herald]]|archive-date=2013-02-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130218001838/http://www.herald.ie/entertainment/around-town/look-who-just-popped-in-for-the-late-late-1902767.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或者是簡寫成為「LLS」<ref name="Celebrity chef and comedians for LLS (6 November 2009)">{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/arts/2009/1106/thelatelateshow.html|title=Celebrity chef and comedians for LLS|date=6 November 2009|accessdate=6 November 2009|publisher=[[Raidió_Teilifís_Éireann|RTÉ]]|archive-date=2010-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100226065143/http://www.rte.ie/arts/2009/1106/thelatelateshow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Boyzone singer to join Tubridy on LLS (13 November 2009)">{{cite news|url=http://www.rte.ie/arts/2009/1113/thelatelateshow.html|title=Boyzone singer to join Tubridy on LLS|date=13 November 2009|accessdate=13 November 2009|publisher=[[Raidió_Teilifís_Éireann|RTÉ]]|archive-date=2010-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100226072335/http://www.rte.ie/arts/2009/1113/thelatelateshow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是目前世界上播放時間最長且由同一主持人進行的[[脱口秀|脱口秀]]節目<ref>{{cite book|last=Lalor|first=Brian|title=The Encyclopedia of Ireland|archive-url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofir0000unse_y9i3|year=2003|publisher=[[Yale_University_Press|Yale University Press]]|isbn=978-0-300-09442-8|url=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediaofir0000unse_y9i3/page/1218 1218]|page=147}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.eurovision.tv/page/news/belgrade-2008?id=1128|title=Dima performs at The Late Late Show|date=31 May 2008|accessdate=4 September 2010|work=[[Eurovision|Eurovision]]|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225144334/http://www.eurovision.tv/page/news/belgrade-2008?id=1128|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/7848737.stm|title=Paisley on RTE's Late Late Show|date=24 January 2009|accessdate=4 September 2010|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225144424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/7848737.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8045336.stm|title=Late Late show getting new face|date=12 May 2009|accessdate=4 September 2010|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225144531/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/8045336.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2009/0602/breaking69.htm|title=Kenny's final viewer figures released|date=2 June 2009|accessdate=4 September 2010|work=The Irish Times|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225144707/http://www.irishtimes.com/news/kenny-s-final-viewer-figures-released-1.841358|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Questions are sometimes raised over whether ''The Tonight Show'' on US television, which began broadcasting in 1954, should be described as the longest running. However there is little continuity between the show launched in 1954 and the current format, with the show existing under different guises and names ('Tonight' and 'Tonight! America after Dark' are just two of its names in its early years). The show in its different formats ran as a variety show, then as a news show that was modelled on breakfast show, before adopting the current format and the name ''The Tonight Show'' when [[Johnny_Carson|Johnny Carson]] took over as permanent presenter in October 1962, some months after ''The Late Late Show'' was launched. Having kept the same name and format continuously, ''The Late Late Show'' is perceived in the media as more entitled to the term "the longest running show".</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.herald.ie/entertainment/around-town/tubridy-has-last-laugh-with-radio-phonein-1741656.html|title=Tubridy has last laugh with radio phone-in|date=16 May 2009|accessdate=30 July 2009|work=[[Evening_Herald|Evening Herald]]|archive-date=2012-08-01|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120801054012/http://www.herald.ie/entertainment/around-town/tubridy-has-last-laugh-with-radio-phonein-1741656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時這也是[[愛爾蘭共和國|愛爾蘭共和國]]政府國營的廣播機構[[愛爾蘭廣播電視|愛爾蘭廣播電視]]其主要節目內容<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/7848737.stm|title=Paisley on RTE's Late Late Show|date=24 January 2009|accessdate=7 September 2009|work=BBC News|archive-date=2015-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150225144424/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/northern_ireland/7848737.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該節目是以現場直播2個多小時的形式，在每年5月至9月期間的星期五晚間21時30分於電視上播出。包含海外地區在內都將《深夜秀》視為愛爾蘭共和國的重要電視節目<ref name="'Just call me Nell'">{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2004/nov/22/biography.gayrights|title='Just call me Nell'|date=22 November 2004|accessdate=13 April 2009|publisher=The Guardian|location=London|first=Angelique|last=Chrisafis|archive-date=2012-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120409234131/http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2004/nov/22/biography.gayrights|dead-url=no}}</ref>，甚至被視為「愛爾蘭脫口秀」<ref name="Why Sinead O'Connor proved a mixed blessing for Ireland's chat show">{{cite news|author=Rob Brown|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4156/is_19990516/ai_n13939084/|title=Why Sinead O'Connor proved a mixed blessing for Ireland's chat show|date=16 May 1999|accessdate=19 September 2009|publisher=[[Sunday_Herald|Sunday Herald]]|archive-date=2010-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100115053427/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4156/is_19990516/ai_n13939084/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

